metadata.name: Probably Nothing Genesis NFT
metadata.description: Congratulations, you are holding one of a very limited number of Probably Nothing Genesis NFTs, your key to unlocking the Probably Nothing ecosystem! Everything we develop will be enhanced by holding a Genesis NFT including boosted rewards, Non-Fungible Experiences (NFEs) and early access to our upcoming product release. [Join our Discord](https://discord.gg/probably0) to learn more about the Original Probably Nothing.
